Package: simBioData
Type: Package
Title: Simulation of Biological and Ecological Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Tage", "Olsen",
      email = "taols9096@uib.no",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package provides a small selection of flexible simulation functions for generating biologically realistic datasets commonly used in ecology and evolutionairy biology.
  It supports a wide range of different datatypes, including count, binomial, longitudinal, phylogenetic, spatial, multi variate and zero-inflated data, making the package useful for power analysis, method development and teaching.
